Your favorite superhero Super Ellie has left her home to save the world. This mission is a little bit different so she has approached you to seek for help. Would you think that you are the best guy for this project? Join Super Ellie Saving The City and be prepared to help this super woman to get ready for a special mission in a way like never before!

This superhero is blessed with the amazing superpowers and strengths so it will definitely be a great honor to find some chick and stylish outfits for her. Give her a nice eye mask with some lovely color that will be enough to represent her identity! Select a pink and purple dress with a heart print on the top and some ruffles on the asymmetric skirt!

Make sure to poof some lovely glitter into the air to make the environment a bit cozy. Take a picture with her team in the end! Now she is ready to save the world.
